room_title: Escape room "Shenandoah Redemption" by The Lock Houston in Houston
room_address: 26797 Hanna Rd #5&6, Oak Ridge North, TX 77385
room_description: Escape an Alcatraz-like prison or the warden will make sure you never leave! Remember, escaping the multiple cells isn't the end of it. Can you also escape the prison without getting caught? With the warden distracted for an hour, this is your prime opportunity to make your escape attempt!
